  <refsect2 id="method-gtksourcelanguage--get-name">
    <title>gtksourceview.SourceLanguage.get_name</title>
    <programlisting><methodsynopsis language="python">
	  <methodname>get_name</methodname>
	  <methodparam></methodparam>
	  </methodsynopsis></programlisting>
      
    <variablelist>
	    <varlistentry>
	      <term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&nbsp;:</term>
	      <listitem><simpara>	the name of <parameter>language</parameter>.</simpara></listitem>
	    </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para>
      The <methodname>get_name</methodname>() method returns the localized name of the language.
	  </para>
  </refsect2>


  <refsect2 id="method-gtksourcelanguage--get-section">
    <title>gtksourceview.SourceLanguage.get_section</title>
    <programlisting><methodsynopsis language="python">
	  <methodname>get_section</methodname>
	  <methodparam></methodparam>
	  </methodsynopsis></programlisting>
      
    <variablelist>
	    <varlistentry>
	      <term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&nbsp;:</term>
	      <listitem><simpara>	the section of <parameter>language</parameter>.</simpara></listitem>
	    </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para>
      The <methodname>get_section</methodname>() method returns the localized section of the language. 
      Each language belong to a section (ex. HTML belogs to the Markup section)
	  </para>
  </refsect2>

  <refsect2 id="method-gtksourcelanguage--get-tags">
    <title>gtksourceview.SourceLanguage.get_tags</title>
    <programlisting><methodsynopsis language="python">
	  <methodname>get_tags</methodname>
	  <methodparam></methodparam>
	  </methodsynopsis></programlisting>
      
    <variablelist>
	    <varlistentry>
	      <term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&nbsp;:</term>
	      <listitem><simpara> a list of <link linkend="class-gtksourcetagstyle"><classname>gtksourceview.SourceTagStyle</classname></link> 
        objects.</simpara></listitem>
	    </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para>
      The <methodname>get_tags</methodname>() method Returns a list of tags for the given <parameter>language</parameter>. 
      You should unref the tags and free the list after usage.
	  </para>
  </refsect2>

  <refsect2 id="method-gtksourcelanguage--get-escape-char">
